Package eu.europa.ec.eurostat.java4eurostat.base

Class StatsHypercube

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.europa.ec.eurostat.java4eurostat.base.StatsHypercube
  • public class StatsHypercube
extends Object
    A hypercube of statistical values. A hypercube has several dimensions. For each dimension, several values are possible. An element of the hypercube is statistical value, whose position in the hypercube is described by its dimension values.
    Author:
    julien Gaffuri
